19:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Ada is best suited for enterprise support, high volume teams, global companies, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. LiveChat AI, meanwhile, shines for e commerce, sales teams, support agents, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2016, Ada describes itself as \"AI-powered customer service automation platform for enterprise-scale support.\" LiveChat AI, established in 2002, positions itself as \"Premium live chat platform with AI-powered chatbot and e-commerce integrations.\" With 14 years between them, LiveChat AI brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Ada offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
1a:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Ada** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0), more features (9 vs 8). However, this does not mean LiveChat AI is a poor choice — far from it. LiveChat AI excels in its own right, particularly for e commerce and sales teams.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value highly accurate ai resolution, go with Ada. If mature and reliable live chat matters more to you, LiveChat AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
